  "prompt": "How do you if you are unhappy?",
  "response": "Here are some signs that might indicate you're unhappy:\n\n1. Emotional indicators:\n- Frequent feelings of sadness or emptiness\n- Lack of motivation or enthusiasm\n- Feeling constantly stressed or anxious\n- Feeling numb or disconnected\n- Irritability or mood swings\n\n2. Behavioral signs:\n- Withdrawing from social activities\n- Loss of interest in hobbies or things you used to enjoy\n- Changes in sleep patterns (sleeping too much or too little)\n- Changes in appetite\n- Difficulty concentrating\n- Procrastination\n\n3. Physical symptoms:\n- Low energy levels\n- Unexplained aches and pains\n- Frequent headaches\n- Digestive issues\n- Weakened immune system\n\n4. Mental indicators:\n- Negative self-talk\n- Pessimistic outlook\n- Feeling stuck or trapped\n- Constantly comparing yourself to others\n- Feeling unfulfilled\n\n5. Relationship signs:\n- Strained relationships\n- Difficulty connecting with others\n- Feeling lonely, even when surrounded by people\n\nIf you consistently experience these signs, it might be helpful to:\n- Talk to a trusted friend or family member\n- Consider professional counseling\n- Practice self-care\n- Identify potential sources of unhappiness\n- Make positive life changes",
